-- Copper Advances for a Second Day in London Trading on Dollar: LME Preview
-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 2010-09-23T06:30:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/copper-climbs-for-a-second-day-in-london-trading-on-dollar-lme-preview.html
Copper rose for a second day in
London as the dollar weakened, making commodities cheaper for
buyers using other currencies. Zinc, nickel and lead advanced.  Market News:  Metals News:  To contact the reporter on this story:
